# Package boundaries

- Library in `src/nlp_shap/` — experiments, papers, GUI elsewhere
- User-facing workflows in `examples/` as lightweight Jupyter notebooks (see `examples.mdc`)
- Add modules only with real implementation, never empty package trees
- Heavy runtime stacks (torch, transformers) → optional extras when introduced
